summary: ...DEPRESSION NOW MOVING SLOWLY NORTHWARD... ...HEAVY RAINS CONTINUE OVER PORTIONS OF EASTERN CUBA AND THE BAHAMAS, WITH WINDS SOON INCREASING OVER THE BAHAMAS... As of 11:00 AM EDT Sun Sep 28 the center of Nine was located near 23.5, -77.3 with movement N at 7 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1002 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
